# pdnd_producer_delegation (Resource)

Creates a PDND producer delegation. The delegation starts in WAITING_FOR_APPROVAL state and must be accepted by the delegate.

Note: Delegations cannot be deleted via the API. Destroying this resource removes it from Terraform state only.

